definition: (literary) to fracture (a bone)/(literary) to cut/to hack/variant of 銼|锉[cuo4]
to sit/to take a seat/to take (a bus, airplane etc)/to bear fruit/variant of 座[zuo4]
to cut the corpse of a criminal into pieces

sentences.english: Beveling can be done by using a coarse file or, preferably, a beveling tool.
sentences.chinese: 坡口可以用粗齿锉做出，或者更好的，用去角刀。

sentences.english: File off both bores to the hexagon of the insertion bushing using a needle-point file.
sentences.chinese: 用细锉将两个孔锉成镶入衬套的六边形。

sentences.english: Iron sharpeneth iron, so a man sharpeneth the countenance of his friend.
sentences.chinese: 朋友互相砥砺，有如以铁锉铁。

sentences.english: Root canal preparation with nickel titanium alloy engine file.
sentences.chinese: 镍钛合金机用锉根管预备。

sentences.english: After cutting her nails, she used an emery board to make the rough edges smooth.
sentences.chinese: 在修剪指甲后，她用指甲锉将边缘锉平。

sentences.english: The owner's name marked on this cigarette lighter has been filed away by the thief.
sentences.chinese: 主人刻在打火机上的姓名被小偷用锉刀锉掉了。

sentences.english: We also scheme out a diagram showing relationship between two stridulatory file types.
sentences.chinese: 对潜蝇科内两类音锉型的关系作了图解。

sentences.english: The cutting of the nickel-titanium hand instruments on curved root canals was unbalanced.
sentences.chinese: 手用镍钛锉对弯曲根管的各部位切割很不均衡。

sentences.english: He files the nail between innings, and soaks it after games.
sentences.chinese: 他在每局之间修锉指甲，并在赛后浸泡它。

sentences.english: Then I used the rotary rasp to, you know, V it out.
sentences.chinese: 然后我使用旋转锉，你知道，让它有V型。

sentences.english: The sharp corners of the table have been rasped off.
Aluminium files are primarily for filing aluminium, aluminium alloy and may be used on other non-ferrous metals.
sentences.chinese: 主要是为了锉削铝材，铝合金，及其他非有色金属上。

sentences.english: He filed away at the metal bar.
She never bothered to file her nails: she just clipped them.
sentences.chinese: 即‘她懒得用指甲锉，历来都是用指甲钳’。

sentences.english: Disclosed is a novel bone file which belongs to medical instrument technical field.
sentences.chinese: 新型骨锉，属于医疗用具技术领域。

sentences.english: The engine numbers were filed away.
sentences.chinese: 发动机的号码被锉掉了。
